PRINTL
PRINTFORML [0] C감각: {ABL:TARGET:0}   [1] B감각: {ABL:TARGET:1}
PRINTFORML [2] V감각: {ABL:TARGET:2}   [3] A감각: {ABL:TARGET:3}
PRINTL
PRINTFORML [10] 신뢰: {ABL:TARGET:10}   [11] 욕망: {ABL:TARGET:11}
